OL,3,CWhole life terms: If government wanted
OL,4,Cto change the law, they could
OL,6,FITV News' Deputy Political Editor
OL,7,FAnushka Asthana looks at the debate
OL,8,Fthat has continued over whether there
OL,9,Fshould be a change in the law so that
OL,10,Funder 18s who commit such atrocities
OL,11,Fcan receive whole-life sentences
OL,13,FThe murder of three little girls at a
OL,14,FTaylor Swift themed dance class in
OL,15,FSouthport is shocking, distressing,
OL,16,Fsickening and extreme. That is why it
OL,17,Fis understandable that Axel
OL,18,FRudakubana's heinous crime - and
OL,19,Fsentencing - has led to an outcry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
