OL,6,FThe reason is simple: the only way to
OL,7,Fimprison someone forever is to impose
OL,8,Fa "whole life order" and while Tories
OL,9,Freduced the age of eligibility for
OL,10,Fthis sentence from 21 to 18, in order
OL,11,Fto apply it to a perpetrator in the
OL,12,FManchester bombing, it is not
OL,13,Favailable for those below 18.
OL,15,FRudakubana committed this atrocity
OL,16,Fnine days before his 18th birthday.
OL,18,FToday, the Conservatives called for
OL,19,Fthe law to change so that - in
OL,20,Fexceptional circumstances like this
OL,21,Fone - a whole life tariff could apply.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
