OL,6,FIn fact, the previous Government was
OL,7,Fgoing through a similar process in its
OL,8,Fattempts to circumvent human rights
OL,9,Fchallenges to its Rwanda policy.
OL,11,FEven on this issue - the fairness of
OL,12,Fwhole life tariffs - the Government
OL,13,Fwas challenged over the case of mass
OL,14,Fmurderer Myra Hindley, and won. As one
OL,15,Fsource put it "international law is a
OL,16,Fliving instrument... It can be
OL,17,Ftested". They said the right of a
OL,18,Fchild perpetrator has to be balanced
OL,19,Fagainst the rights of a child victim.
