OL,6,FThere are plenty of more liberal
OL,7,FConservative figures who would agree.
OL,8,FThe former Tory Attorney General
OL,9,FDominic Grieve told us that the reason
OL,10,Ffor the law is the belief that
OL,11,Fchildren - unlike adults - can change
OL,12,Fin adulthood. And if Rudakubana fails
OL,13,Fto? He will remain in prison after 52
OL,14,Fyears.
OL,16,FOthers pointed out that the sentence
OL,17,Fis unique - way bigger than for
OL,18,Fprevious child killers. The boys who
OL,19,Fmurdered 2 year old James Bulger were
OL,20,Fsentenced to a minimum of eight years
OL,21,Fbefore becoming eligible for parole.
